ger|advertisingIdentifier\"\napps/waketask-iphone/.agents/skills/release-review/privacy-checklist.md:217:- [Apple Privacy Guidelines](https://developer.apple.com/app-store/app-privacy-details/)\napps/waketask-iphone/.agents/skills/release-review/privacy-checklist.md:218:- [Privacy Manifest](https://developer.apple.com/documentation/bundleresources/privacy_manifest_files)\napps/waketask-iphone/.agents/skills/release-review/privacy-checklist.md:219:- [App Tracking Transparency](https://developer.apple.com/documentation/apptrackingtransparency)\napps/waketask-iphone/.agents/skills/release-review/distribution-checklist.md:85:<string>We need camera access to scan QR codes.</string>\napps/waketask-iphone/.agents/skills/release-review/distribution-checklist.md:93:<string>We need your location to show nearby stores.</string>\napps/waketask-iphone/.agents/skills/release-review/distribution-checklist.md:97:<string>We need microphone access for voice messages.</string>\napps/waketask-iphone/.agents/skills/release-review/distribution-checklist.md:101:<string>We need contacts access to help you invite friends.</string>\napps/waketask-iphone/.agents/skills/release-review/distribution-checklist.md:348:- [ ] Push notifications work (if applicable)\napps/waketask-iphone/.agents/skills/release-review/api-design-checklist.md:249:var pingRequest = URLRequest(url: healthCheckURL)\napps/waketask-iphone/SwiftAIBoilerplateProUITests/PaywallFlowUITests.swift:162:        let termsLink = app.buttons.matching(\napps/waketask-iphone/SwiftAIBoilerplateProUITests/PaywallFlowUITests.swift:163:            NSPredicate(format: \"label CONTAINS[c] 'terms'\")\napps/waketask-iphone/SwiftAIBoilerplateProUITests/PaywallFlowUITests.swift:166:        if termsLink.waitForExistence(timeout: 5) {\napps/waketask-iphone/SwiftAIBoilerplateProUITests/PaywallFlowUITests.swift:167:            XCTAssertTrue(termsLink.exists)\napps/waketask-iphone/SwiftAIBoilerplateProUITests/PaywallFlowUITests.swift:174:        let p